## 1. FROZEN NORTH STAR

> **The following paragraph is FROZEN. It is the fixed reference against which every arc below is
> measured. It is not revised by any later arc; later arcs are measured against it, never the
> reverse.**

ORIGINAL INTENT (frozen, from `Build_Docs/where_i_got_stuck.md` ~2026-05-15, corroborated by the
earliest reports task000-task023 and the two earliest handoffs `session_handoff_v4_substrate.md` /
`session_handoff_v4_curvature_pivot.md`): Will Lloyd was studying standard physics identities
(gravitational redshift, special-relativistic time dilation) that both reduce to the same shape — a
quantity depending on the square root of something that goes to zero at a boundary (the horizon;
lightspeed). He wrote the SAME physics as a constraint that should evaluate to EXACTLY zero by
construction, expressed two algebraically-identical ways (one routed around a squaring operation,
one around the square root), evaluated both across a matched sweep in floating point, and examined
the residuals. Observed: (Obs1) the two forms behave completely differently — one identically zero
everywhere, the other nonzero on ~half the points; (Obs2) the nonzero residuals look
structured/self-similar ("fractal" — a gut reaction, not a claim); (Obs3, most confident) the
residuals sit on a discrete DOUBLING ladder, each rung ~2x the one below; (Obs4) the silent form is
silent because of the arithmetic PATH (bit-level self-cancellation), not because the physics is
trivial — both forms do the same physics; (Obs5) more algebraically-equivalent routes produce more
distinct residual fingerprints; (Obs6) residual amplitude is not flat — it changes near the
boundary; (Obs7, the one he could not let go of) residuals scale with precision by what looks like
an EXACT ratio between precisions — lawful, not noise-like. He built the V4 typed substrate (typed
results, explicit refusal, provenance, no hidden rescue) as the foundation to study this properly,
but lacked the METHOD: a measurement technique that gets under the arithmetic noise floor, recovers
the real structure without disturbing it, and that he can trust enough to answer Q5. The six open
questions (verbatim/paraphrased): **Q1** What is the thing casting these patterns? — only the shadow
on the float grid is ever seen, never the object. **Q2** Why does the route through the expression
matter so much? — what property of a path selects which rounding survives vs cancels? **Q3** Why is
the residual ladder a doubling ladder (factor-of-two rung spacing)? — measurable but underived.
**Q4** What is the boundary actually doing to the amplitude? — there is an envelope near the
horizon/lightspeed he cannot characterise. **Q5 (the one that actually stops him)** Is the structure
a real property of the phenomenon, or an artefact of the measurement? — instrument and object may be
entangled and he has no way to separate "this is real" from "this is the measurement." **Q6** The
tooling wall — the current method can DETECT that structure is there but cannot RESOLVE it finer than
the arithmetic noise floor; the instrument is too coarse. This is the fixed reference against which
every later arc is measured.

> **END FROZEN NORTH STAR.**

